snippet.title: Nothing cheers you up more than funny animals - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Animals just never fail to cheer us up and make us laugh. Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, goats, turkeys, parrots, camels, ostriches, bears... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things... So funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:

"Monkeys Spinning Monkeys" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
